{"tid":2393890,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–大芋在哪","createTime":"2021-02-03T22:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T10:32:57.000Z","uid":38861,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3a95b5ee433d382cc1c228e66396bf74c3bfb7","tid":2393890,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T22:28:27.000Z","msg":"芋頭除了用在臘味煲之外，它的葉子亦有著神奇的作用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YK0vDN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YK0vDN.jpg&h=f3841d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）跟蓮花的葉子一樣，芋頭葉具有防水的功能，水珠會在葉上呈水珠狀，並不會散開變成水灘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJDwCiQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJDwCiQ.png&h=0c2616f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）但與蓮花葉不同的是，芋頭葉的表面是呈類似蜂巢狀的結構，而蓮花葉則為梅花間竹式的突起柱狀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EBJ1e5y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEBJ1e5y.png&h=e32f0ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖4）科學家參照芋頭葉的結構，製作出表面為六角形的結構物料，裡頭包含著非常複雜的算式。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AME0vDV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAME0vDV.png&h=65fe8dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而用上不同的力度將水珠撞擊到仿芋頭葉的物料上，水珠亦沒有散開濺成水灘，成功從大自然間的事物中借鏡及活用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=73da86f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=37dec78d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-020-57410-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41598-020-57410-2&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=b391f0e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-020-57410-2</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://mnsl-journal.springeropen.com/articles/10.1186/2213-9621-1-6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmnsl-journal.springeropen.com%2Farticles%2F10.1186%2F2213-9621-1-6&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=d5d0a24a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mnsl-journal.springeropen.com/articles/10.1186/2213-9621-1-6</a>"},{"pid":"2089207cfe883dadce5465137b492ca695f2b899","tid":2393890,"uid":34119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T22:53:17.000Z","msg":"就咁鋪層graphene喺平面又唔知有冇同樣效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a644604cdb91eadc22467e92fb94d5b57be7a5","tid":2393890,"uid":3422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T23:46:50.000Z","msg":"離題一問，英國最新嘅變種話接種過疫苗嘅人可能更易被感染，同薯巴你之前講嘅ADE有冇關係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7349eedd6496d579164327e3eaa44a3fe9f086b","tid":2393890,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T00:06:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=